c) Two-dimensional “global” PIC simulations (fully kinetic ions and electrons) of the curved shock and associated ion foreshock region have been performed by Savoini et al. (2013) and Savoini and Lembège (2015). Because of computational constraints, the analyses were restricted to the Q⊥ region (90∘>ΘBn>45∘\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
