				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$B_{z}$\end{document} polarity, but with a clear preference for clock angles between 40∘\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
